Package org.tedros.fx.annotation.scene.web

Annotation Type TWebView

  • @Retention(RUNTIME)
@Target(FIELD)
public @interface TWebView
     Build a WebView 
 
 Example: 
 Load an url from web:
 @TWebView(engine=@TWebEngine(load="https://www.tedrosbox.com"))
 private SimpleStringProperty webContent;
 
 Load a content from the file system:
 @TWebView(engine=@TWebEngine(loadContent="file:c://usr/index.html"))
 private SimpleStringProperty localContent;
    Author:
    Davis Gordon

         WebView Class
 
  Sets the value of the property fontSmoothingType. 
  Property description: Specifies a requested font smoothing type : gray or LCD.
